'''理查德·埃克斯利'''（{{lang-en|'''Richard Eckersley'''}}，{{bd|1989年|3月12日|catidx=Eckersley, Richard}}），是[[英格兰|英格兰]][[职业|职业]][[足球|足球]][[运动员|运动员]]，能够司职左右边后卫，出身[[曼联|曼联]][[曼聯預備隊及青訓學院|青訓系統]]。他的哥哥是曾效力曼聯的[[亚当·埃克斯利|亚当·埃克斯利]]。

== 生平 ==
2009年1月24日，埃克斯利在对阵[[托特纳姆热刺|托特纳姆热刺]]的[[英格兰足总杯|英格兰足总杯]]中首次代表曼联出场正式比赛，替换了同样是第一次出赛的[[法比奥·达·席尔瓦|法比奥]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7842634.stm |title=Man Utd 2-1 Tottenham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-24 |accessdate=2009-03-02 |archive-date=2009-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090126030941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7842634.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，三天后他又在对[[西布罗姆维奇|西布罗姆维奇]]的比赛中获得了第一次联赛出场的机会<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7844603.stm |title=West Brom 0-5 Man Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] sport |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2009-03-02 |archive-date=2009-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090128092829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7844603.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年7月15日埃克斯利拒絕曼聯提供的新合約，轉投新升[[英超|英超]]的[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，雖然無約在身，由於未滿24歲，般尼仍需支付補償金，金額有待兩會商討<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8151844.stm |title=Burnley sign defender Eckersley |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] sport |date=2009-07-15 |accessdate=2009-07-16 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210222540/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8151844.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。最終曼聯收取50萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]及附加分紅，在解決轉會費問題後，僅為般尼在盃賽上陣3場的埃克斯利獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]護級球會[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]1個月汲取上陣經驗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_6003232,00.html |title=Eckersley to join Pilgrims |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-03-04 |accessdate=2010-03-05 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035544/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_6003232,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，在4場正選上陣後，於4月1日獲延長借用至球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_6069530,00.html |title=Pilgrims extend Eckersley deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-04-01 |accessdate=2010-04-02}}</ref></small>，期間合共上陣7場。

2010年11月12日埃克斯利再被外借到[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|巴拉福特]]直到翌年1月3日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9184031.stm |title=Bradford City sign Kiernan & Eckersley on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-12 |accessdate=2010-11-13 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805140259/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9184031.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣6場並獲延長借用至2月6日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9346025.stm |title=Bradford City agree new loan deals with trio |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-06 |accessdate=2011-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307065536/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9346025.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於上陣12場後借用期滿返回般尼<ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.bradfordcityfc.co.uk/page/News/0,,10266~2287934,00.html |title=Loan duo leave the Bantams |publisher=[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|''bradfordcityfc.co.uk'']] |date=2011-02-07 |accessdate=2011-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327090150/http://www.bradfordcityfc.co.uk/page/News/0%2C%2C10266~2287934%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-03-27 }}</ref>。2011年3月14日他再被外借到另一支[[英乙|英乙]]球隊[[貝里足球俱樂部|貝利]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bury/9424709.stm |title=Richard Eckersley joins Bury on loan from Burnley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-14 |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307050152/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bury/9424709.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於上陣3場後，在4月15日被般尼提前召回，再借用到[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美職聯]]球會[[多倫多足球俱樂部|多倫多FC]]直到2012年1月，他與前[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]領隊[[保羅·馬連拿|保羅·馬連拿]]異地重逢，兩人曾在普利茅夫共事，而保羅·馬連拿現時在多倫多FC擔任球員發展總監<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6873195,00.html |title=Toronto take Eckersley |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-04-15 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-date=2011-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419092529/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6873195,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣23場<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.torontofc.ca/players/richard-eckersley |title=Richard Eckersley |publisher=[[多倫多足球俱樂部|''torontofc.ca'']] |accessdate=2012-02-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211103522/http://www.torontofc.ca/players/richard-eckersley |archivedate=2012-02-11 }}</ref>。

2012年1月26日埃克斯利與般尼提前解除尚餘18個月的合期，加盟兩年多僅在盃賽上陣4場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16745238 |title=Burnley defender Richard Eckersley leaves club |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-01-26 |accessdate=2012-02-19 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213154007/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16745238 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

